.000Z","msg":"[突發]有政府工會帶頭呼籲罷工！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390073\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390073</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"94f52c5a5912f37c2b30ba0439312c88cb6af8b7","tid":1389984,"uid":184216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:19:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fc38745fdb80499728bee30305da892b73506f5","tid":1389984,"uid":287844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:20:12.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人&nbsp;<br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷&nbsp;<br />\n#罷工罷市罷課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71772eafa4188135be96303fe3676c613cc5a5a8","tid":1389984,"uid":275887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:23:21.000Z","msg":"推。"},{"pid":"0570e7df41e234b4b2311f88bb2071604aff6647","tid":1389984,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:24:38.000Z","msg":"航空界帶頭睇嚟可以發到好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />1"},{"pid":"540a2d87e7df2e8ef062192d459366ef462746e4","tid":1389984,"uid":275243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:26:05.000Z","msg":"管理不善而導致國際排名節節下跌的香港正苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5b56d998e18465b2d7d46d72402b45fbc3161b","tid":1389984,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:27:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5679a8cee0352f560a4da5108bb2410460daeb6","tid":1389984,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:28:49.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"579b6a82f08b2c03328c8f2d93cc717088a52d23","tid":1389984,"uid":260715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T06:29:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2910231ca38c6f44547d9911078b96807f6